                <note rend="inline" type="source">884.6461 Tsana Dam/402: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Egypt (<persName type="to">Jardine</persName>)</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-06-01T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >June 1, 1933—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>12. White Engineering Corporation requests you cable status Tsana proposal.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
